components.name: CardComponent

styleUrlsData.data:
.cs-card
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif
    padding: 10px
    border-radius: 5px
    border-width: thin
    display: block
    max-width: 100%
    outline: none
    text-decoration: none
    transition-property: box-shadow, opacity
    overflow-wrap: break-word
    position: relative
    white-space: normal
    background-color: #FFFFFF

    &-shadow
        box-shadow: 0 2px 1px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, .2), 0 1px 1px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, .14), 0 1px 3px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, .12) !important

styleUrlsData.data:
@import "../../assets/styles/sass/colors"
@import '~material-design-icons/iconfont/material-icons.css'


.cs-input-container
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif
    display: flex

    align-items: center
    position: relative

i

    &:focus + .fa
        color: $mainBlue

    &::placeholder
        color: $mediumGray

components.name: SwitchComponent

styleUrlsData.data:
@import "../../assets/styles/sass/colors"

.cs-switch
    position: relative
    display: inline-block
    width: 64px
    height: 32px

    & input
        opacity: 0
        width: 0
        height: 0

.cs-slider
    position: absolute
    cursor: pointer
    top: 0
    left: 0
    right: 0
    bottom: 0
    border: 1px solid $mediumGray
    background-color: $white
    -webkit-transition: .4s
    transition: .4s


    &:before
        position: absolute
        content: ""
        height: 24px
        width: 24px
        left: 4px
        bottom: 3px
        background-color: $mediumGray
        -webkit-transition: .4s
        transition: .4s


    input:checked + &
        background-color: $mainBlue
        border: 1px solid $mainBlue


    input:checked + &:before
        -webkit-transform: translateX(26px)
        -ms-transform: translateX(26px)
        transform: translateX(26px)
        background-color: $white
        left: 8px

    &.cs-round
        border-radius: 34px


    &.cs-round:before
        border-radius: 50%

components.name: TablesComponent

styleUrlsData.data:
@import "../../assets/styles/sass/colors"

.cs-table-roll
  display: inline-block
  width: 100%
  height: calc(100% - 30px)
  margin-top: 2px

table
  font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif
  width: 100%
  table-layout: fixed
  border-collapse: collapse

  thead tr
    height: 30px

    th
      text-align: left
      font-size: 12px
      color: $darkestGray

  tbody
    tr
      height: 40px
      border-bottom: 1px solid #CCCCCC

    tr:last-child
      border-bottom: none

    td
      font-size: 14px
      text-align: left
      vertical-align: middle
      white-space: nowrap
      text-overflow: ellipsis
      overflow-wrap: break
      padding: 8px 8px 8px 0


.input-search
  padding-bottom: 16px
  width: 250px

.cs-colum-sortble
  cursor: pointer
